title: “Ocean’s 8” Isn’t Up to the Talents of Its Stars
description: Richard Brody reviews “Ocean’s 8,” which stars Sandra Bullock, Cate Blanchett, Rihanna, Anne Hathaway, and others in a gender-swapped reboot of “Ocean’s Eleven.”
